@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
skinparam classBorderColor #6A1B9A
[*] --> Closed
Closed --> Active : reject
Active --> Reviewed : process
Active : entry / log attendance
Reviewed --> Pending : approve
Pending --> Created : update
Created --> Archived : reject
Created : entry / log attendance
Archived --> [*]
@enduml